<div class="flex-container w-full">
  <!-- Header -->
  <header class="bg-custom-four text-white p-4">
    <div class="flex justify-center items-center">
      <img
        src="images/headshot.jpg"
        class="h-auto max-w-xxs rounded-full"
        alt="A professional picture of Alex wearing a light blue sweater and smiling at the camera."
      />
    </div>
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Alex Beeken</h1>
      <p class="text-sm">Senior Software Engineer</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <main class="container mx-auto p-4">

    <!-- Introduction -->
    <section class="my-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Introduction</h2>
      <p>
        Hello! I'm Alex Beeken, a Senior Software Engineer with <%= ((Date.today - Date.new(2015, 6, 1)) / 365.25).to_i %> years of professional experience.
      </p>
      <br>
      <p>
        I started coding in 2013 for fun by taking <a class="text-blue-500" href="https://cs50.harvard.edu/x/2023/">Harvard's CS50x class</a>. In 2014 I decided to abandon my career as a high school choir teacher and pursue coding full time. I attended <a class="text-blue-500" href="http://epicodus.com">Epicodus</a> in the winter of 2015 and got a job through that internship. Since graduating I've been delivering value fulltime to different organizations which you can see listed under the experience section. 
      </p>
      <br>
      <p>
        On top of my full time gigs I also spent a summer working for the <a class="text-blue-500" href="https://www.monolake.org/">Mono Lake Committee</a> in their bookstore and tourist information center. On my freetime that summer I volunteered some time to build them an information kiosk app using Ember.js for an unused touchscreen and ran it locally on an old laptop they had lying around. The old machine eventually broke down in 2022. However, while it was running it enhanced the educational content of a very important non-profit in the conservation world!
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Skills -->
    <section class="my-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Skills</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
        <li>Ruby on Rails</li>
        <li>Postgres</li>
        <li>MongoDB</li>
        <li>Elasticsearch</li>
        <li>React</li>
        <li>Ember</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- Experience -->
    <section class="my-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Experience</h2>

      <% @experience.each do |job| %>
        <div class="group ease-in-out hover:max-h-[50rem] min-h-[8rem] md:min-h-[4rem] lg:min-h-[4rem] duration-800 transition-[max-height] p-4 max-h-0">
          <div class="flex justify-left items-left mb-3">
            <img
              src=<%= job['logo'] %>
              class="max-h-xxxs max-w-xxxs rounded-full mr-2"
              alt="A picture of the <%= job['company'] %> logo."
            />
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium"><b><%= job['company'] %></b> - <%= job['position'] %> - <%= job['period'] %></h3>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="group-hover:block hidden" >
            <div class="grid gap-3 s:grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
              <% job['responsibilities'].each do |item| %>
                <div class="border-2 rounded-lg border-custom-two opacity-40 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity p-4 h-auto">
                  <%= item %>
                </div>
              <% end %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </section>

    <!-- Education -->
    <section class="my-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Education</h2>
      <% @education.each do |school| %>
        <div class="mb-4">
          <p><b><%= school['institution'] %></b></p>
          <p><%= school['description'] %></p>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact -->
    <section class="my-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Contact Info</h2>
      <p>aeb242@gmail.com</p>
      <a class="text-blue-500" href="http://www.linkedin.com/in/alexbeeken">LinkedIn</a>
    </section>
  </main>
</div>
